<div class="page-header centered">
    <h2 class="page-title">Health Education & Awareness</h2>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Learn how to prevent water-borne diseases</p>
</div>

<div class="education-layout">
    <div class="modules-sidebar">
        <h3 class="sidebar-title">Learning Modules</h3>
        <div class="modules-list">
            <a href="/education?module=hygiene&lang=<%= language %>" 
               class="module-item <%= activeModule === 'hygiene' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <div class="module-content">
                    <h4 class="module-title">Hand Hygiene & Sanitation</h4>
                    <p class="module-description">Proper handwashing techniques and sanitation practices</p>
                    <div class="module-meta">
                        <span class="duration">15 min</span>
                        <span class="status completed">Completed</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/education?module=water&lang=<%= language %>" 
               class="module-item <%= activeModule === 'water' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <div class="module-content">
                    <h4 class="module-title">Safe Water Practices</h4>
                    <p class="module-description">Water purification and storage methods</p>
                    <div class="module-meta">
                        <span class="duration">20 min</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/education?module=symptoms&lang=<%= language %>" 
               class="module-item <%= activeModule === 'symptoms' ? 'active' : '' %>">
                <div class="module-content">
                    <h4 class="module-title">Symptom Recognition</h4>
                    <p class="module-description">Early identification and when to seek help</p>
                    <div class="module-meta">
                        <span class="duration">10 min</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-content-area">
        <div class="module-header">
            <h3 class="module-active-title">
                <% if (activeModule === 'hygiene') { %>Hand Hygiene & Sanitation<% } %>
                <% if (activeModule === 'water') { %>Safe Water Practices<% } %>
                <% if (activeModule === 'symptoms') { %>Symptom Recognition<% } %>
            </h3>
            <div class="module-actions">
                <button class="action-btn primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
                    Start Module
                </button>
                <button class="action-btn secondary">
                    <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
                    Download
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="module-body">
            <% if (activeModule === 'hygiene') { %>
            <div class="module-image">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1020012/pexels-photo-1020012.jpeg" 
                     alt="Hand washing demonstration" class="content-image">
            </div>
            <div class="module-text">
                <p>Proper hand hygiene is the most effective way to prevent water-borne diseases. Follow these essential steps:</p>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>Wet hands with clean, running water (warm or cold)</li>
                    <li>Apply soap and lather by rubbing hands together</li>
                    <li>Scrub all surfaces for at least 20 seconds</li>
                    <li>Rinse thoroughly and dry with a clean towel</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <% if (activeModule === 'water') { %>
            <div class="module-image">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1191710/pexels-photo-1191710.jpeg" 
                     alt="Water purification" class="content-image">
            </div>
            <div class="module-text">
                <p>Safe water practices can prevent most water-borne infections. Use these methods to ensure water safety:</p>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>Boil water for at least 1 minute before drinking</li>
                    <li>Use water purification tablets as directed</li>
                    <li>Store treated water in clean, covered containers</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <% if (activeModule === 'symptoms') { %>
            <div class="module-image">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/263402/pexels-photo-263402.jpeg" 
                     alt="Healthcare consultation" class="content-image">
            </div>
            <div class="module-text">
                <p>Early recognition of symptoms can save lives. Watch for these warning signs:</p>
                <div class="warning-box">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Seek immediate medical help if you notice:</h4>
                    <ul class="warning-list">
                        <li>Severe dehydration (dry mouth, no tears, dizziness)</li>
                        <li>Blood in stool or vomit</li>
                        <li>High fever with severe abdominal pain</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="community-impact">
            <div class="impact-header">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                <h4>Community Impact</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="impact-stats">
                <div class="impact-stat">
                    <div class="impact-number">2,847</div>
                    <div class="impact-label">People Trained</div>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-stat">
                    <div class="impact-number">156</div>
                    <div class="impact-label">Villages Reached</div>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-stat">
                    <div class="impact-number">89%</div>
                    <div class="impact-label">Disease Reduction</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    initializeEducation();
});
</script>